folder: Pacific Street & Rochester Avenue, Brooklyn, NY
text:
Pacific Street, east from Rochester Avenue. Behind the fence, on the south side of the street, are being erected Kingsborough Houses, a low-rent housing project of the New York City Housing Authority.

View 2 is southwestward across the grounds of the housing development.

October 24, 1940
Views 1,2

P. L. Sperr
